    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 powerplant. This unit boasts a flawlessly maintained VANOS system and individual throttle bodies that provide instantaneous throttle response up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with mechanical precision, paired with a factory-spec variable M differential lock for optimal power distribution. The chassis is structurally immaculate, with documented subframe reinforcement and a suspension refresh utilizing OEM bushings to preserve its legendary handling dynamics. Finished in a preserved factory coat with zero oxidation, this is a mechanically superior example for the discerning purist.",
