      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and boasts its original factory finish with zero imperfections, scratches, or swirl marks. The interior remains in pristine condition, featuring untouched leather upholstery, flawless trim, and a cabin that still retains its original scent. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach; it has been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a complete, documented history provided. Every electronic component and luxury feature functions perfectly. Included with the sale are all original manuals, two sets of keys, and the original window sticker. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a truly immaculate, investment-grade example.",
